Program: Discovery
Title: New Bush Babies
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrw60
Last Broadcast Date: 28 March 1994
Four new species of bush babies have been discovered in Africa - but could there be many more? Also the chair of parapsychology at Edinburgh University, Professor Robert Morris, explains why he believes psychic powers: News from the International Rise Research Institute in the Philippines about higher yielding rice. Presented by Ruth Linton. Show less